if u want happniness,u are better find a faith,which proves u deserve alive.

my family
it is almost faith of most chinese.it is our nature and our families directly decide whether we are happy in the daily life.
family is my faith no.1.

science fanaticism.
science is my faith no.2,because i can release my value which make me really happy.

ccp.
in my view,the essential of ccp is seek rejuvenation for the chinese nation and happiness for the chinese people,which also is my dream and in my interest.
so i decide to join ccp.
but the principle is justice and fair,and seek for a bright future for the whole world in a long term.
it's my faith no.3 .

wealth
if u have wealth,you have freedom.
